<h3 id="government-spending-and-revenue">Government spending and revenue</h3>

<p>Chart 1 shows public spending by main function. Total Managed Expenditure (<abbr title="Total Managed Expenditure">TME</abbr>) is expected to be around £928 billion in 2020-2021.</p>

